se.hig.dvg329.algomaze.model

Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • se.hig.dvg329.algomaze.model.Cell

  • public class Cell
extends java.util.Observable
    The Cell class represent cells of a Maze. The may also be thought of the nodes or squares of a Maze. Each Cell holds x and y coordinates as well as information about which of its wall are tore down and which are still erect. Each Cell can be marked with a value that can be used by other classes to assign specific values to represent some state of the Cell.
